title: Episode 14: Russell Dickerson
description:
On today's episode, Kailey sits down with everyone's favorite guest, her husband Russell Dickerson! Kailey and Russell chat about all the new and crazy things happening in their life. They share about their  most recent travels to Europe, life on tour, and current season of walking in faith and what is ahead!
